N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 255.67 - Storage and handling of plastic pipe and associated components

State Regulations

Each operator must have and follow written procedures for
the storage and handling of plastic pipe and associated components that meet
the applicable listed specifications. Notes
